  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to a world of suspicion, deception and busy bodies. Welcome to <strong>Dahlia View</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548750/extras/5d94a7fca8da95881aa17bacdcce978b.poster.avif?t=1773660826\" width=616 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548750/extras/5d94a7fca8da95881aa17bacdcce978b.webm?t=1773660826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548750/extras/5d94a7fca8da95881aa17bacdcce978b.mp4?t=1773660826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by 1950’s cinema, White Paper Games brings you a detective thriller with twists, turns and accusations in a case that’s taken the attention of an entire neighbourhood. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A girl has gone missing and your neighbours are acting suspiciously. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play the role of a retired detective, a detective that shouldn’t be on the case, but who can’t help themselves. You <i>need </i>to find the truth, a truth that will cause close relationships to fracture. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You know from years of experience that when a child goes missing, it’s often the people closest that know something. Since they won’t give you the answers, you must take matters into your own hands. When a girl’s life is at stake, etiquette goes out the window.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How do you find the missing child?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>By Spying</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have the perfect view from your window, take that opportunity to spy on your neighbour’s daily activities to see if they’re hiding anything suspicious.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548750/extras/241398a2838e287387fda56a77c4341a.poster.avif?t=1773660826\" width=616 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548750/extras/241398a2838e287387fda56a77c4341a.webm?t=1773660826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548750/extras/241398a2838e287387fda56a77c4341a.mp4?t=1773660826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>By Breaking and Entering</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You see something that piques  your curiosity, you can’t help yourself. Break into areas you have no business being, pick locks that your neighbours think will protect their secrets, maybe take an item or two, for evidence of course…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548750/extras/783975b77cc105020a070f1f5ef2f0bc.poster.avif?t=1773660826\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548750/extras/783975b77cc105020a070f1f5ef2f0bc.webm?t=1773660826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548750/extras/783975b77cc105020a070f1f5ef2f0bc.mp4?t=1773660826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>By making your own deductions in classic detective style</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We’re not holding your hands here. You’re the detective, you have the evidence, now how does it connect? We’ll leave that to you to figure out</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548750/extras/b4a51085e00ae315facd4941604d8463.poster.avif?t=1773660826\" width=616 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548750/extras/b4a51085e00ae315facd4941604d8463.webm?t=1773660826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548750/extras/b4a51085e00ae315facd4941604d8463.mp4?t=1773660826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A young girl’s life is at risk. Wouldn’t you do anything you could to return her to her family?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to a world of suspicion, deception and busy bodies. Welcome to <strong>Dahlia View</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548750/extras/5d94a7fca8da95881aa17bacdcce978b.poster.avif?t=1773660826\" width=616 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548750/extras/5d94a7fca8da95881aa17bacdcce978b.webm?t=1773660826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548750/extras/5d94a7fca8da95881aa17bacdcce978b.mp4?t=1773660826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by 1950’s cinema, White Paper Games brings you a detective thriller with twists, turns and accusations in a case that’s taken the attention of an entire neighbourhood. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A girl has gone missing and your neighbours are acting suspiciously. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play the role of a retired detective, a detective that shouldn’t be on the case, but who can’t help themselves. You <i>need </i>to find the truth, a truth that will cause close relationships to fracture. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You know from years of experience that when a child goes missing, it’s often the people closest that know something. Since they won’t give you the answers, you must take matters into your own hands. When a girl’s life is at stake, etiquette goes out the window.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How do you find the missing child?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>By Spying</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\