tective style</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We’re not holding your hands here. You’re the detective, you have the evidence, now how does it connect? We’ll leave that to you to figure out</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548750/extras/b4a51085e00ae315facd4941604d8463.poster.avif?t=1773660826\" width=616 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548750/extras/b4a51085e00ae315facd4941604d8463.webm?t=1773660826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548750/extras/b4a51085e00ae315facd4941604d8463.mp4?t=1773660826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A young girl’s life is at risk. Wouldn’t you do anything you could to return her to her family?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
